nested_items.name: AmazonForecastRoleArn
nested_items.description: The IAM role that Canvas passes to Amazon Forecast for time series forecasting. By default, Canvas uses the execution role specified in the UserProfile that launches the Canvas application. If an execution role is not specified in the UserProfile, Canvas uses the execution role specified in the Domain that owns the UserProfile. To allow time series forecasting, this IAM role should have the AmazonSageMakerCanvasForecastAccess policy attached and forecast.amazonaws.com added in the trust relationship as a service principal.

nested_items.description: An array of Amazon Resource Names (ARNs) of the IAM roles that the execution role of SageMaker can assume for performing operations or tasks related to Amazon EMR clusters or Amazon EMR Serverless applications.
